content.title: 中国語：79,212人の受験者が2018年9月に教員免許試験に合格する -  INQUIRER.net
教師のための79,000パスの9月の2018年のボード試験 -  ABS CBNのニュース
content.desc: ABS CBN News MANILA- A total of 79, 212 passed the licensure examination for teachers given last September, the Professional Regulation Commission (PRC) announced Friday. The PRC said 18,409 elementary teachers out of 90,750 examinees and 60,803 secondary teachers out of 126,582 examinees passed the exams. Of the elementary teachers who passed, 17,200 are first timers and 1,209 are repeaters. For the secondary teachers, 52,453 passers are first timers and 8,350 are repeaters.
